<L>__{interior another palace corridor day 1780's}
<A>__{mozart and arco walk side by side. they pass salieri who is staring at mozart in fascination. as they disappear, he steals toward the music stands, unable to help himself.}
<C>__{mozart}
<D>__{well, i think that went off remarkably well, don't you?}
<C>__{arco}
<D>__{indeed.}
<C>__{mozart}
<D>__{these viennese certainly know good music when they hear it.}
<C>__{arco}
<D>__{his grace is very angry with you.}
<C>__{mozart}
<D>__{what do you mean?}
<A>__{they arrive at the door of colloredo's private apartment.}
<C>__{arco}
<D>__{you are to come in here and ask his pardon.}
<A>__{arco opens the door.}
